LockTest::lock
├── When amount is zero
│   └── It should revert with ZeroAmount
├── When user has insufficient unlocked balance
│   └── It should revert with InsufficientBalance
├── When lock manager has no existing allowance
│   └── It should revert with LockDoesNotExist
├── When new amount exceeds allowance
│   └── It should revert with InsufficientAllowance
└── When valid parameters
    ├── It should increase the locked amount
    └── It should emit LockAmountChanged